    "Mobile Health Monitoring:Wearable health gadgets, such as fitness trackers and medical sensors, use lightweight cryptography.",
    "As these devices often operate on small batteries, protecting sensitive medical information must rely on lightweight encryption.",
    "Users may now keep tabs on their health without worrying about compromising the privacy of their medical records.",
    "Intelligent Power Grids:The transfer of data and control instructions between smart metres, grid equipment, and the centralised grid management system in smart grid systems is encrypted using lightweight cryptography.",
    "These low-power cryptographic systems protect data authenticity and privacy with little re-source drain."
